    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's not a perfect combo, but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle lol. just like, a single glass of wine to take the edge off while the pill kicks in. wouldn't a tiny bit just make the diazepam work a little more effectively so i don't lie awake for hours? it feels like it would just enhance the relaxing effect rather than doing anything crazy.",
