      "content": "but i really need to sleep tonight, i cant deal another day like this. if i just stick to a very small amount, like a couple sips, it's basically just a way to boost the effect right? it's not like im going to pass out from two sips and a pill. can't i just use it as a little extra help to ensure i actually drift off?",
